<L>__{exterior buckingham palace inner courtyard day}
<A>__{the inner courtyard of buckingham palace. in a ritual unchanged since queen victoria, a uniformed piper, wearing a kilt of ancient hunting stuart tartan, marches under her majesty's windows, playing the bagpipes. t's her morning alarm call, and it's the way she wakes up wherever she is anywhere in the world.}
